/DuaLipa-changes-choreography-slipping-on-sweat-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-changes-choreography-slipping-on-sweat-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-changes-choreography-slipping-on-sweat-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-changes-choreography-slipping-on-sweat-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>透露，她在出汗后被迫改变了现场的一些编舞。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">杜阿·利帕（Dua Lipa）——“激进乐观”评论：夏季但轻微的心理流行</a></strong></li></ul><p>在最近接受<em>SiriusXM</em>采访时，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">“激进乐观”</a>歌手说：“我在巡演中摔倒了，我想在巴塞罗那一次，在米兰一次，在同一个地点，那只是欧洲最热的一周（来自<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/173754/Dua-Lipa-changes-choreography-after-slipping-on-sweat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐新闻）</em></a> ）。</p><p> “所以我的一些舞者只是多出了一点汗。所以我在一个小汗水洼上滑倒了，我们不得不改变编舞，这样我就不会在我要开始跳舞的地方流上一滩汗水。”</p><p>利帕接着说，这种舞台上的事故是巡演时“体验的一部分”，并补充道：“你一定会受点伤。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-she-manifested-headlining-glastonbury-with-her-third-album-3752590">这位流行歌星谈到了她在职业生涯早期如何“通过专辑三”“展现”格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的主角</a>。下个月，利帕将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">登上金字塔舞台</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tame-impalas-kevin-parker-pays-tribute-to-absolute-weapon-dua-lipa-on-release-of-mind-blower-new-album-radical-optimism-3753362">Tame Impala 的 Kevin Parker 在与 Lipa 合作制作了她的第三张专辑《Radical Optimism》后对她进行了赞扬</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752809" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752809" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752809" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg" alt="杜阿·利帕新闻图片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/DuaLipa-Credit-Tyrone-Lebon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752809" class="wp-caption-text">杜阿·利帕.图片来源：蒂龙·勒邦</figcaption></figure><p><em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">对该唱片的三星级评论</a>中写道：“这张专辑的海滩氛围非常适合音乐节现场的无忧无虑的氛围。你只是希望这些歌曲能多一点。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-cover-cleo-sols-sunshine-in-radio-1-live-lounge-3754309"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-adds-european-headline-shows-to-summer-2024-radical-optimism-tour-3602852">下个月在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节之前举行的一系列欧洲演出</a>之后，利帕将于今年十月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-announces-one-off-london-show-at-royal-albert-hall-buy-tickets-3608988">在伦敦历史悠久的皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅举办的一场一次性音乐会上</a>展示她的新作品。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dua-lipa-and-chris-stapleton-perform-think-im-in-love-with-you-at-the-academy-of-country-music-awards-3757273">Lipa 最近与 Chris Stapleton 合作现场表演了“Think I&#39;m In Love With You”</a> 。她还被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-and-harry-styles-in-uks-richest-people-under-40-list-3757258">列为英国40岁以下最富有的人之一</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-forced-to-change-choreography-after-slipping-on-sweat-3758024">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 因出汗而被迫改变编舞，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
